{"id":409209,"date":[{"year":1960,"month":8,"day":27}],"page":"3","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"300","ytitle":"","mtitle":"增产短笛","ftitle":"","authors":["戚永芳"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"松江县新五公社社员　戚永芳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脱粒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跃进战鼓震天响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"丰收喜报贴满墙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"稻子堆得宝塔高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢乐歌声万里扬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轧稻机，隆隆响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"块块场地谷满场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轧净晒干归进仓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金光冲天千里香。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"除草和积肥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多除一次草，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多长一级稻；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多积一担肥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多收一斤宝；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杂草除干净，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"稻苗节节高。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肥料积得多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粮仓堆满稻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"施肥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人穿新衣样子好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"稻施肥料换容貌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脱掉黄衣换绿袍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生长发育嫩娇娇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嫩娇娇，嫩娇娇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"棵棵变成灵芝草。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"养猪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万物生长，全靠太阳；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田里庄稼，要靠肥长。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一亩一猪，猪多增粮；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粮多猪多，国富民强。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田间管理"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳不出花不红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田间管理莫放松。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高田水浆均匀溉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"低田注意起漏洞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缺口加高岸筑阔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"防风、雨、潮三弟兄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抓时间，产粮食，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一亩千斤满堂红!"}]}